{"tid":1872350,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"湖北二氧化硫污染爆錶 網民：燒1.4萬屍體才有這濃度","createTime":"2020-02-10T04:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T11:08:02.000Z","uid":222970,"like":116,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8b8240c8ab1e3aed30e6ab3e06ab4447ed28f9","tid":1872350,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>湖北二氧化硫污染爆錶 網民：燒1.4萬屍體才有這濃度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjRa3Rk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjRa3Rk.jpg&h=05893bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民發現昨晚武漢市二氧化硫濃度爆錶（右），質疑與當地可疑大火，及大量火化遺體有關。　<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情失控，中共公佈的疫情數字不透明，特別是死亡人數。有網民在天氣數據網站，發現武漢的二氧化硫（SO₂）污染爆錶，由於這種氣體通常是燃燒有機物產生，有網友推測是因為疫情下焚燒大量屍體造成，更推算如果要產生高濃度的二氧化硫，恐怕要焚燒1.4萬具屍體才有可能。<br />\n<br />\n全球交互式天氣網站「Windy」的數據顯示，武漢市充滿大量二氧化硫，全市每立方米的濃度均超過80微克，武漢市各行政區都難以倖免，昨晚7時許，更出現每立方米1,700微克的驚人濃度，湖北省其他城市也飄散着這種氣體。<br />\n<br />\n有關發現在網上論壇Reddit成為熱門話題，網民追查二氧化硫最濃的位置，發現距離當地公墓、灰砂磚廠相當近，懷疑與當局處理不治病人屍體有關，網民更推算，火化1.4萬具遺體，才會釋放這量的二氧化硫，亦有網民與前晚當地出現多個可疑的火警聯想起來。<br />\n<br />\n武漢當局早前要求死家屬，要簡化因武漢肺炎不治的病人的身後事，當地的殯儀館則被要求提供每日24小時服務。網上早前有片段顯示，武漢的殯儀館堆滿等候火化的遺體。<br />\n<br />\n晚上10時，Windy網站顯示，武漢二氣化硫濃度約每立方米400微克，而當局公佈的數字，武漢至今有14,982個確診病例，608人死亡。<br />\n<br />\nSource<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200209/XCDDCPMSCBSAP5RNBLKBRV6PSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200209%2FXCDDCPMSCBSAP5RNBLKBRV6PSE%2F&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=e38e1694\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200209%2FXCDDCPMSCBSAP5RNBLKBRV6PSE%2F&h=4ad0d40f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200209/XCDDCPMSCBSAP5RNBLKBRV6PSE/</a><br />\n<br />\n其他詳盡source<br />\n<a href=\"https://ntdtv.com/b5/2020/02/09/a102773335.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F02%2F09%2Fa102773335.html&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=8bc10f03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ntdtv.com/b5/2020/02/09/a102773335.html</a></strong>"},{"pid":"1ede06eb7ba12a74400051a7bc43227cf2be98f3","tid":1872350,"uid":222970,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:51:12.000Z","msg":"火光紅紅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/russian_market/status/1225087706289573888?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frussian_market%2Fstatus%2F1225087706289573888%3Fs%3D21&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=da792d62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frussian_market%2Fstatus%2F1225087706289573888%3Fs%3D21&h=64484376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/russian_market/status/1225087706289573888?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FEkWeZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFEkWeZ2.jpg&h=53787a5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"051132c81fc69ce174f421ad9daa24e77c68a3cb","tid":1872350,"uid":70256,"like":10,"dislike":16,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:52:04.000Z","msg":"唔排除燒垃圾"},{"pid":"750ab4732d09b2039dbc6102663d3e11da86fc4d","tid":1872350,"uid":228894,"like":118,"dislike":2,"score":116,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"x農兄弟 : 這隻武漢人發高燒, 已經沒救, 只好拿去河邊烤了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df2304225b02bb7fe9602ad742d18aff0055255","tid":1872350,"uid":347497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"燒山話係燒垃圾。"},{"pid":"732200770baff20610bcbef6654744e5b4aac000","tid":1872350,"uid":224066,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.lamatruth.com/fanti/common/upload/2013/05/27/11103